(106, 231, 'Photobooth (en)', 'form-builder', '<div class="entry post clearfix">\r\n<h1 class="title">Photobooth</h1>\r\n<h1><a href="http://kis-photomegroup.fr/WordPress3/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/img_starbooth1.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-827" title="img_starbooth" src="http://kis-photomegroup.fr/WordPress3/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/img_starbooth1.png" alt="" width="439" height="324" /></a></h1>\r\n<h2>Re-inventing the photobooth</h2>\r\n<p>&gt; Stylish design by Philippe Starck<br /> &gt; Compliant with international passport standards<br /> &gt; External LCD screen for advertisement &amp; attraction<br /> &gt; New fun products</p>\r\n<h2>Revolutionary and innovative booth</h2>\r\n<p><strong>Setting a new standard</strong></p>\r\n<p>Philippe Starck is proposing a timeless and distinctive booth while optimizing customer experience and ergonomics.</p>\r\n<p><strong>State-of-the-art features</strong></p>\r\n<p>The internal touchscreen brings simplicity and usability to the booth. The seat is fixed and backlit from inside. The camera is adjusted automatically to the customer’s height. With the brand new user interface, customers can enjoy more comfort and readability. An SQL database records all photobooth activities for statistical analysis.</p>\r\n<p><strong>New range of fun products</strong></p>\r\n<p>Pop art photos, postcards, world tour fun photos, funny simple and multiple frames, and more!</p>\r\n<p><strong>Social networks</strong></p>\r\n<p>Linked to Facebook, Picasa allowing users to upload their fun products on their personal account.</p>\r\n<p>Additionally, the picture can be sent by e-mail or saved on a USB stick.</p>\r\n<div class="content-center" style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto;">{imageshow sl=1 sc=3 h=400 /}</div>\r\n<p class="content-center"><em>JSN ImageShow with Theme Classic</em></p>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 20, '2012-11-09 02:44:31', 42, '', '2014-02-11 10:51:40', 838, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-11-09 02:44:31', '0000-00